    "en": {
      "title": "12 Indian fishermen arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "12 Indian fishermen have been arrested with their boat for the crime of cross-border fishing in Sri Lankan waters.",
        "They were arrested by the navy on Sunday evening on the beach of Parutthurai and detained at the Kangesanturai naval base.",
        "The arrested fishermen will be arraigned today in the Puducherry Court through the officials of the Water Resources Department. (R)"
      ],
